name: The Witcher 2077
description:
Loving the Witcher 3 right now as the last DLC drops soon, got me wondering what if they kept up with the whole Witcher thing into the far future, seeing as their next RPG is Cyber Punk 2077 I decided to mix the two smiley
Roach is now a spaceship, no doubt he will get stuck in a sun or veer into an asteroid for no reason.
